# Fold.csr -- registry for "A singular fold model for capacity-constrained
# dynamics" (v74). Machine-readable mirror of the paper's own Claim Status
# table (Table 1): proved results carry state proved / method theorem; the
# paper's explicitly-open items are type open_problem. One symbol, one
# definition home; hashes pin the deposited PDF.

